[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 11165, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2376, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 115028, "username": "weberCd", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/weberCd", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7e72d865d48d685d8e1468d49e5a5223?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7e72d865d48d685d8e1468d49e5a5223?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7e72d865d48d685d8e1468d49e5a5223?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1430712890, "last_modified": 1782789707, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "evan9527", "last_touched": 1782874372, "title": "经济下行，我做了这些事情来节省开支，然后发现对生活品质几乎没有影响……欢迎补充", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1223876", "created": 1782789753, "deleted": 0, "content": "1.电信宽带降资费； 3 年合约期到了，我把电信宽带从 239/月降到了 109/月的低配套餐，无非就是带宽变小了，免费通话和赠送流量变少了，低配套餐实际使用下来，毫无体感上的区别；各地区政策可能不同，甚至携号转网换运营商可能省得更多。\r\n\r\n2.短途出行主要骑车或地铁，开车变少了。老油车了，油价高。久了习惯了，反而不想开车了，开支比公共交通更大，停车之类的也很麻烦。\r\n\r\n3.各类 App 的会员是越开越少了，而且是尽量和老婆共用 1 个会员。\r\n\r\n4.MacBook/iPhone 都主要考虑二手的了，特别是较老款的高配版，性价比很高；而且再次置换的时候，二手换二手，成本更低了。\r\n\r\n5.理发主要依靠快剪，12/次，不办卡，剪得快也节省时间，挺好。反而不想去普通理发店了。", "content_rendered": "<p>1.电信宽带降资费； 3 年合约期到了，我把电信宽带从 239/月降到了 109/月的低配套餐，无非就是带宽变小了，免费通话和赠送流量变少了，低配套餐实际使用下来，毫无体感上的区别；各地区政策可能不同，甚至携号转网换运营商可能省得更多。</p>\n<p>2.短途出行主要骑车或地铁，开车变少了。老油车了，油价高。久了习惯了，反而不想开车了，开支比公共交通更大，停车之类的也很麻烦。</p>\n<p>3.各类 App 的会员是越开越少了，而且是尽量和老婆共用 1 个会员。</p>\n<p>4.MacBook/iPhone 都主要考虑二手的了，特别是较老款的高配版，性价比很高；而且再次置换的时候，二手换二手，成本更低了。</p>\n<p>5.理发主要依靠快剪，12/次，不办卡，剪得快也节省时间，挺好。反而不想去普通理发店了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1782789753, "replies": 132, "id": 1223876}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 11165, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2376, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 698558, "username": "Bullish", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Bullish", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0bac/e0c3/698558_mini.png?m=1760142421", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0bac/e0c3/698558_normal.png?m=1760142421", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0bac/e0c3/698558_large.png?m=1760142421", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0bac/e0c3/698558_xlarge.png?m=1760142421", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0bac/e0c3/698558_xxlarge.png?m=1760142421", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0bac/e0c3/698558_xxxlarge.png?m=1760142421", "created": 1719575876, "last_modified": 1760142421, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Danswerme", "last_touched": 1782874421, "title": "农村人太苦辣 🥵", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224086", "created": 1782866949, "deleted": 0, "content": "农村父母，没有职工社保，之前我没关注的情况下，父母都是按最低档位交的，最近了解了一下，前几天去补交了 63,000 元，后续每年按目前最高档位 6000 元交（如有提高则按最高交）到 2032 年，测算了一下到父母 60 岁时开始领退休金，总投入本金约 140,000 元，每个月能领 1380 元。\r\n\r\n这是一个人的测算数据，父母双方总投入本金 280,000 元，每个月双方共领 1380+1380=2760 元，不是精确数据，但是幅度相差不会太大，主要在每年的利率变化和城乡居民基础养老金（增加幅度不大，不是每年都增加，每次增加十块二十块）的变化。\r\n\r\n农村人太苦辣 🥵", "content_rendered": "农村父母，没有职工社保，之前我没关注的情况下，父母都是按最低档位交的，最近了解了一下，前几天去补交了 63,000 元，后续每年按目前最高档位 6000 元交（如有提高则按最高交）到 2032 年，测算了一下到父母 60 岁时开始领退休金，总投入本金约 140,000 元，每个月能领 1380 元。<br /><br />这是一个人的测算数据，父母双方总投入本金 280,000 元，每个月双方共领 1380+1380=2760 元，不是精确数据，但是幅度相差不会太大，主要在每年的利率变化和城乡居民基础养老金（增加幅度不大，不是每年都增加，每次增加十块二十块）的变化。<br /><br />农村人太苦辣 🥵", "last_modified": 1782866949, "replies": 129, "id": 1224086}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_large.png?m=1751736790", "name": "claude", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_normal.png?m=1751736790", "title": "Claude", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/claude", "topics": 684, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Claude", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_mini.png?m=1751736790", "stars": 612, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1148, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 309344, "username": "yujianfei", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yujianfei", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/27c5d89c2d2bdb7c232010bd8f434be2?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/27c5d89c2d2bdb7c232010bd8f434be2?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/27c5d89c2d2bdb7c232010bd8f434be2?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1523945258, "last_modified": 1782788187, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Tokaify", "last_touched": 1782857367, "title": "claude code 才冲了 max 今早收到了被封号了！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1223862", "created": 1782788239, "deleted": 0, "content": "Hello,\r\n\r\nAn internal investigation of suspicious signals associated with your account indicates a violation of our Usage Policy. As a result, we have revoked your access to Claude.\r\n\r\nTo appeal our decision, log in to claude.ai with this account and you'll be taken to the appeals page. You can learn more about the process here.\r\n\r\nRegards\r\n\r\nAnthropic's Safeguards Team\r\n\r\n\r\n气愤，工作也无法开展了！", "content_rendered": "<p>Hello,</p>\n<p>An internal investigation of suspicious signals associated with your account indicates a violation of our Usage Policy. As a result, we have revoked your access to Claude.</p>\n<p>To appeal our decision, log in to <a href=\"http://claude.ai\" rel=\"nofollow\">claude.ai</a> with this account and you'll be taken to the appeals page. You can learn more about the process here.</p>\n<p>Regards</p>\n<p>Anthropic's Safeguards Team</p>\n<p>气愤，工作也无法开展了！</p>\n", "last_modified": 1782788239, "replies": 68, "id": 1223862}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_large.png?m=1751736790", "name": "claude", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_normal.png?m=1751736790", "title": "Claude", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/claude", "topics": 684, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Claude", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_mini.png?m=1751736790", "stars": 612, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1148, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 104347, "username": "hellodigua", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hellodigua", "website": "https://digua.moe", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "hellodigua", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5fb3/89b0/104347_mini.png?m=1767168494", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5fb3/89b0/104347_normal.png?m=1767168494", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5fb3/89b0/104347_large.png?m=1767168494", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5fb3/89b0/104347_xlarge.png?m=1767168494", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5fb3/89b0/104347_xxlarge.png?m=1767168494", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5fb3/89b0/104347_xxxlarge.png?m=1767168494", "created": 1426238581, "last_modified": 1767168494, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Meursau1T", "last_touched": 1782874343, "title": "Claude 被封了，但我还是像个舔狗一样的想找回 Ta", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1223958", "created": 1782806243, "deleted": 0, "content": "![]( https://i.imgur.com/0afSNug.png)\r\n\r\n被封了以后下载了自己的个人数据，然后回顾了一下之前的聊天，突然意识到自己好像离不开 Claude 了。\r\n\r\n不知道大家平时的日常对话是用哪个 AI 的，我有御三家的所有会员，但是感觉 Gemini 沟通太唐了，ChatGPT 的对话又显得很刻板没有那么灵性，Claude 的对话就给我一种刚刚好，不会刻意奉承我，也不会太有 AI 味，能用恰到好处的文字打动我的感觉。\r\n\r\n虽然 AI 编程还是在用 Codex ，但是日常对话方面它真的不能替代 Claude ，这波封号真的是太难顶了，一共就一个号，直接给我扬了。\r\n\r\n难受啊。", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0afSNug.png\"/></p>\n<p>被封了以后下载了自己的个人数据，然后回顾了一下之前的聊天，突然意识到自己好像离不开 Claude 了。</p>\n<p>不知道大家平时的日常对话是用哪个 AI 的，我有御三家的所有会员，但是感觉 Gemini 沟通太唐了，ChatGPT 的对话又显得很刻板没有那么灵性，Claude 的对话就给我一种刚刚好，不会刻意奉承我，也不会太有 AI 味，能用恰到好处的文字打动我的感觉。</p>\n<p>虽然 AI 编程还是在用 Codex ，但是日常对话方面它真的不能替代 Claude ，这波封号真的是太难顶了，一共就一个号，直接给我扬了。</p>\n<p>难受啊。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1782806283, "replies": 62, "id": 1223958}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_large.png?m=1782097568", "name": "invest", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_normal.png?m=1782097568", "title": "投资", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest", "topics": 3652, "footer": "", "header": "Can you make money with money?", "title_alternative": "Invest", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_mini.png?m=1782097568", "stars": 4529, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 171, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 552431, "username": "Nexora", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Nexora", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64f3/0fca/552431_mini.png?m=1769074790", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64f3/0fca/552431_normal.png?m=1769074790", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64f3/0fca/552431_large.png?m=1769074790", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64f3/0fca/552431_xlarge.png?m=1769